ComicInfo.Title: Moving Targets, Conclusion
ComicInfo.Summary:
END OF STORY ARC!
“MOVING TARGETS,” Conclusion
An exhausted Jack is trapped in Texas surrounded by MegaChurch Cops, assassins, and spies that want him dead. With technocrat hunter-killer drones on his tail, it doesn’t seem like Jack can survive this one… until he flies the Analog skies in a vintage war machine. Don’t miss the end of the exciting second collection—not everyone’s gonna make it!
